# Day 1 â€“ Introduction to Cybersecurity

## Objective
The objective of Day 1 is to understand what cybersecurity is, why it exists,
and how it plays a critical role in protecting digital systems and data.

## Topics Covered
- Introduction to Cybersecurity
- Why Cybersecurity is Important
- Cybersecurity vs Information Security vs Network Security
- Overview of the Cybersecurity Landscape

## Key Learnings
- Cybersecurity focuses on protecting systems, networks, and data from digital attacks.
- The increasing use of technology has made cybersecurity essential for individuals,
  organizations, and governments.
- Cybersecurity differs from information security and network security in scope,
  but all three work together to ensure overall protection.

## Reflection
This day helped me build a strong foundation by understanding the purpose
and importance of cybersecurity before moving on to technical concepts.

